    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"110087\">Scott Morrison</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/217875-Is-there-code-for-X.3F/topic/equivalence.20of.20fibres.20over.20equal.20base.20points.3F/near/381632354\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>What is</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">foo</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Œ±</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">J</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚Üí</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span> <span class=\"n\">_</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">j</span> <span class=\"n\">j'</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">J</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">j</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">j'</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Œ±</span> <span class=\"n\">j</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚âÉ</span> <span class=\"n\">Œ±</span> <span class=\"n\">j'</span> <span class=\"n\">where</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">toFun</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"n\">congrArg</span> <span class=\"n\">Œ±</span> <span class=\"n\">h</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚ñ∏</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">invFun</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"n\">congrArg</span> <span class=\"n\">Œ±</span> <span class=\"n\">h.symm</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚ñ∏</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">left_inv</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span> <span class=\"n\">aesop</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">right_inv</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span> <span class=\"n\">aesop</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<